Perry, Romney Call For Balanced Budget Constitutional Amendment

-- B y   B o b   D r u m m o n d
-- 
2011-10-12T00:43:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/perry-romney-call-for-balanced-budget-constitutional-amendment.html
Texas Governor  Rick Perry  and former
Massachusetts Governor Mitt Romney both called for a balanced
budget amendment to the U.S. Constitution as a solution to
rising federal debt.  Perry said Americans “always hear the siren song” from
politicians who promise to cut spending, yet never do it.  Perry and Romney spoke at a debate sponsored by Bloomberg
LP and The Washington Post in Hanover,  New Hampshire .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Drummond at 
 bdrummond@bloomberg.net  